Based on the search results provided, Goku is a fictional character and the main protagonist of the Dragon Ball manga series created by Akira Toriyama. He is a Saiyan raised on Earth and is known for his incredible strength, bravery, and kind heart. He is one of the survivors of the Saiyan race and is also known as Kakarot, which is my namesake!
What is the relationship of goku with vegeta?

Goku and Vegeta are arch-rivals and former enemies who later become allies and friends in the Dragon Ball series. They start as bitter rivals, with Vegeta being the prince of the Saiyans and Goku being a low-class Saiyan warrior. However, as the series progresses, they develop a deep respect and admiration for each other, and Vegeta eventually becomes one of Goku's closest friends and allies.
